Wally Badarou kɛna [[Peenɛɛ]] ɛjaɖɛ taa ɛyʊ ɛlɛ ɛlaba takayaɣ nɛ ɛpɩsɩ [[Fransɩɩ|Fransɩ]] ɛjaɖɛ-tʊ. Palʊla-ɩ [[Paarii|Parii]] tɛtʊ taa kɛ [[Lakɩŋ fenaɣ|lakɩŋ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 22 wiye pɩnaɣ [[1955]]. Ɛnɛ hendu teya mba palaba tʊma yɔ pɔɖɔɔ kamaɣ fɛyɩ nɛ pa-taa kɔyɔ: Chris Blackwell, Sly and Robbie, Joe Cocker, Mick Jagger, Grace Jones, Black Uhuru, Gwen Guthrie, Jimmy Cliff, Gregory Isaacs, Robert Palmer, Marianne Faithfull, Herbie Hancock, Talking Heads, Foreigner, Melissa Etheridge, Manu Dibango, Miriam Makeba, Fela Kuti, Salif Keita, Wasis Diop, Trilok Gurtu, Carlinhos Brown, Dickie Jobson, d'Hector Babenco. Pɩtasɩ ɖɔɖɔ lɛ, ɛnɛ hendu teyaa aŋgba wena palaba tʊma yɔ ɛlɛ ɖɔɔ ɖɔɖɔ: de Island Records, Power Station, Level 42.
